=== phone_booth ===
~ triggerMonologue("perception", 6, "The receiver is off the hook. The rain hasn't gotten in yet — it hasn't been long.")
~ triggerMonologue("empathy", 7, "Someone was waiting for a call that never came.")
The phone booth is empty. Receiver hanging loose.
* [Check for a dial tone]
    Dead. The line's been cut.
    -> END
* [Look for a number]
    Someone scratched seven digits into the paint. The last three are gouged out.
